            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        【致敬逆行者：给正在武汉的你<img class="W_img_face" render="ext" src="//img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/02/hot_wuhanjiayou_org.png" title="[武汉加油]" alt="[武汉加油]" type="face" style="visibility: hidden;">】在这座城市，有人初来乍到，有人来了几年，有人立业安家，也有人土生土长…<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E6%AD%A6%E6%B1%89%E6%98%AF%E5%BA%A7%E8%8B%B1%E9%9B%84%E5%9F%8E%23&amp;from=default">#武汉是座英雄城#</a>，因为英雄就在城里面。致敬<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E9%80%86%E8%A1%8C%E8%80%85%23&amp;from=default">#疫情中的逆行者#</a>，给正在武汉的你，给这座英雄城市。<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E5%8A%A0%E6%B2%B9%E6%AD%A6%E6%B1%89%23&amp;from=default">#加油武汉#</a>，加油中国！&nbsp;&nbsp;<a suda-uatrack="key=tblog_card&amp;value=click_title:4468726256746646:1034-video:1034%3A4468724061896740:page_100206_home:2286908003:4468726256746646:2286908003" title="人民网的微博视频" href="http://t.cn/A6Pn3dvy" alt="http://t.cn/A6Pn3dvy" action-type="feed_list_url" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><i class="W_ficon ficon_cd_video">L</i>人民网的微博视频</a> ​​​​                                            </div>
